			<div class="content" id="post-content-3564531">
									

<p>This is part three. It's about that weird intersection between platonic and romantic you sometimes feel between friends. It's also about the lengths people can go to protect the people they love.</p>
<p>The stands in this, imo, rule pretty hard.</p>
<p>Thanks to aideneldritch, scarhaver, fenton-st, communism will win, who read it before I posted it.</p>
<p>I'm the Bomb and Dance Commander are by Electric Six. Jitterbug is, honestly, after the song from the Wizard of Oz. Achy Breaky Heart is, obviously, Billy Ray Cyrus.</p>

