			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3614224">
									

<p>Speaking as a person who is pretty strongly not a fan of JoJo but a major fan of this series&#8230; this isn't JoJo. This is a bunch of murderous AWCY blowhards who pretend they are in JoJo. The Breeder even points out he's ruining the mood when he does it.</p>
